data.description: Nestled along the North Fork River, discover this 3-bedroom plus den home with 2 full baths and a spacious 2-car garage. Its open floor plan is perfect for family and entertainment, with the kitchen offering views of the family room and tranquil river backdrop. It boasts stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, and ample storage. The master suite features a walk-in closet and separated vanity from its bath/shower. Highlights include large tiles, energy-efficient cooling, granite-adorned guest bath, recessed lighting, and hurricane-resistant windows. Located conveniently near a major highway, this home is a riverside jewel.
